{"tid":869003,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"諗住下個月去東京大阪拉麵朝聖, 入黎share下你地去喺嗰到食過最正既拉麵","createTime":"2018-10-20T03:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T03:39:44.000Z","uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a77d1702d393011e594504a51c23e93cf4ed479e","tid":869003,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外問下喺香港有分店嗰啲拉麵店(eg. 無敵家,麺屋一燈)同日本本店質素分別大唔大? <br />\n差唔多既話寧願試下當地獨有既舖頭"},{"pid":"d3ea1eb618fd94565e38541e474fd76fac092d67","tid":869003,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"諗住下個月去東京大阪拉麵朝聖, 入黎share下你地<span style=\"color: red;\">喺</span>嗰到食過最正既拉麵"},{"pid":"87ffa584ad4c374b2cbe319c731c59831a933f5a","tid":869003,"uid":78089,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:25:48.000Z","msg":"麵屋一燈幾好食，不過大排長龍要開門前早去排定隊，個麵好大碗，唔夠食先好再加麵，但個叉燒同個雞就覺得般"},{"pid":"09b838b638bebba5bacc2ac3476ba9a77774fe5a","tid":869003,"uid":129664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:28:18.000Z","msg":"日本既無敵家同香港既無敵家好似冇任何關係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb0a0d68f9a7a055b2d642c679b521466789968","tid":869003,"uid":73381,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"金龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc37f7e353258586b5c5917510e57eec9b778e7f","tid":869003,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09b838b638bebba5bacc2ac3476ba9a77774fe5a","tid":869003,"uid":129664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:28:18.000Z","msg":"日本既無敵家同香港既無敵家好似冇任何關係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:30:48.000Z","msg":"竟然冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔驚俾人告咩?"},{"p