512947fb4502eb178a9cb844eda","tid":869003,"uid":87560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"麥苗<br />\n<a href=\"https://tabelog.com/tw/tokyo/A1315/A131502/13194812/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftabelog.com%2Ftw%2Ftokyo%2FA1315%2FA131502%2F13194812%2F&d=do%2BRgQdsO12VW89BEKWd9DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=42f6ccff\" target=\"_blank\">https://tabelog.com/tw/tokyo/A1315/A131502/13194812/</a>"},{"pid":"c5057ede360afa3bbcc64ae50aae3e90bd0e772d","tid":869003,"uid":61680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce02019b4c101512947fb4502eb178a9cb844eda","tid":869003,"uid":87560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"麥苗<br />\n<a href=\"https://tabelog.com/tw/tokyo/A1315/A131502/13194812/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftabelog.com%2Ftw%2Ftokyo%2FA1315%2FA131502%2F13194812%2F&d=do%2BRgQdsO12VW89BEKWd9DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=42f6ccff\" target=\"_blank\">https://tabelog.com/tw/tokyo/A1315/A131502/13194812/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:21:15.000Z","msg":"麥苗真係好正，不過得一種麵量，佢個叉燒飯300羊，一定叫埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(上次排到差啲趕唔到飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老板娘見我單機排俾我skip咗前面三大grp人入先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"c3da5f4d43fc8d2ee43ee95c0be1292489b7bb3a","tid":869003,"uid":61680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e67e837d50ad40e1699e1251ac053307ae9796e","tid":869003,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"我都想知東京既正野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 新橫濱拉麵博物館有冇伏, 同埋D MINI拉麵=正常幾%, 如果要食哂8間要幾多餐 ?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:32:15.000Z","msg":"冇伏，不過要排好撚耐<br />\nmini 大約 1/3 - 2/5碗，普通食量2碗飽，大盛食量3-4碗(排都排到碌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n之前食過味樂同Yuji，味樂個昆布醬油湯好回味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Yuji個吞拿魚濃湯同魚叉燒真係諗都冇諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過完咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(味樂話係全日本最難去到嘅拉麵鋪：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;搭飛機再轉乘渡輪8小時。總店的營業時間只有2個半小時。堪稱日本第一難？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n不過Yuji本店喺美國，日本冇分店，都唔知邊個難去啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   )"},{"pid":"29056299325f8f2974c5c05d280f9f3ee1b329ad","tid":869003,"uid":61680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:40:36.000Z","msg":"沾麵 道 個沾汁世界級正，濃而不死鹹，滑而不油膩。 缺點係位置，同佢個汁正到覺得啲配料比唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仲可以買雪藏1 pack pack咁買走。煮麻煩少少，但係佢個汁同麵個味同喺佢鋪食冇分別咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(我覺得一燈個汁冇道咁正添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"68580117147393a5a4ba64d9cf013152e38911f3","tid":869003,"uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/184653_7606b812ba9a381a7a9fb08a00d8c6eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F184653_7606b812ba9a381a7a9fb08a00d8c6eb.png&h=e23a0d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/184656_5384561b6d0079a8ed82d1b4f0d7c32b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F184656_5384561b6d0079a8ed82d1b4f0d7c32b.png&h=6caffca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3年前食過幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係奈良富雄站"},{"pid":"d81a5c013fbc959545896e3cd1995a487f337408","tid":869003,"uid":215195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"大阪有間叫沾麵雀 叉燒入口即融<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東京濱機町有間叫thank嘅雞肉拉麵又係正到仆街<br />\n諗起又好想去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968eb5b7ef60dba5eccc50d12e91000cc9ee0211","tid":869003,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"東京：池袋 雞穴，六本木 竹虎"},{"pid":"1b3dc1a799ee63238d209c77d5fd68bf5694deae","tid":869003,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"上次去好失敗地淨係食左神座一間<br />\n但係正既"},{"pid":"4d47ea8268ce94b0692243b5c5812ba76ea14c53","tid":869003,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"食過麵屋一燈<br />\n而家唔洗排到以前咁 有得拎籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次十一點開鋪先去到 排左廿分鐘左右拎籌 佢叫我十二點再返去 跟住去左車站附近商店街行左行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係幾好食但冇個種想像中會好食到嘩一聲嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋真係食到好飽"},{"pid":"cfcdd98728722011f6bc13f7252b465b4899bc1d","tid":869003,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3da5f4d43fc8d2ee43ee95c0be1292489b7bb3a","tid":869003,"uid":61680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e67e837d50ad40e1699e1251ac053307ae9796e","tid":869003,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"我都想知東京既正野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 新橫濱拉麵博物館有冇伏, 同埋D MINI拉麵=正常幾%, 如果要食哂8間要幾多餐 ?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:32:15.000Z","msg":"冇伏，不過要排好撚耐<br />\nmini 大約 1/3 - 2/5碗，普通食量2碗飽，大盛食量3-4碗(排都排到碌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n之前食過味樂同Yuji，味樂個昆布醬油湯好回味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Yuji個吞拿魚濃湯同魚叉燒真係諗都冇諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過完咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(味樂話係全日本最難去到嘅拉麵鋪：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;搭飛機再轉乘渡輪8小時。總店的營業時間只有2個半小時。堪稱日本第一難？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n不過Yuji本店喺美國，日本冇分店，都唔知邊個難去啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   )"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"咁好唔好分2餐/3餐食哂佢 8/9間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為反正橫濱好似只得牛鍋係特別野, 而我又食唔起牛鍋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}